downloadTitle: Microsoft Lync 2010 Adoption and Training Kit: Sample Forms
downloadDescription: This zipped file contains sample forms for use during a Microsoft Lync 2010 pilot program.
detailsSection: This download package contains two HTML templates that you can use to publish forms on your internal pilot site. It includes a "Signup for Lync 2010" form and a sample scenario feedback form.
installInstructionSection: To install the download, save the zipped file to a directory on your computer. After you save it, unzip it by right-clicking the file name, selecting Extract All, selecting a destination where you want the extracted files to reside, and then clicking Extract. To remove the download, delete the file from directory where you saved it.
